1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
(A few months later...)

2
00:00:02,380 --> 00:00:03,130
Hinata.

3
00:00:03,130 --> 00:00:03,960
Yes?

4
00:00:04,170 --> 00:00:04,920
Come over here for a second.

5
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:08,510
Is this the data from last time?

6
00:00:08,510 --> 00:00:09,220
Yes.

7
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:22,730
You got chewed out again, huh?

8
00:00:24,150 --> 00:00:25,610
It's all my fault.

9
00:00:25,610 --> 00:00:26,530
I guess so...

10
00:00:26,530 --> 00:00:27,440
Hinata.

11
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:28,930
Yes?

12
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:30,030
I'm sorry.

13
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:41,040
I'm home.

14
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,380
Welcome back.

15
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:49,670
Hey, you're going to wrinkle your suit.

16
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,840
I'm so tired and hungry.
I just want to sleep.

17
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:56,600
I'll get it ready right now.
Just wait a moment.

18
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:05,860
I haven't seen this tie before.

19
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:08,360
You can't meet clients looking like that.

20
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:11,400
Use mine for today.
